  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women 18 years and older treated with somatostatin analogs

          -  Active acromegaly

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiovascular or cerebrovascular disease

          -  Thrombophlebitis or thromboembolism

          -  Breast cancer

          -  Non-controlled arterial hypertension

          -  Smoking

          -  Pregnancy or lactation
      </textblock>
